asset_contract.name: DEGEN3RATES
asset_contract.description:
MINT YOUR GIVEAWAY PASS HERE https://degen3rates.io/

We do degen stuff... we give away stuff too.. alotta stuff

DEGEN3RATES is a collection of 7,777 Degenerative NFTs, a community project bridging web2 to web3. Bringing trust, truth & transparency to crypto giveaways

Your Degen3rate acts as your membership to our giveaway & raffle community

Mint milestones:
Every 150 minted NFTs .5eth is given back to the community while also a minimum royalty share of 50% is distributed to holders through giveaways, games & airdrops. During mint phase royalties are reduced to 5% meaning 100% of royalties are given back to holders in giveaways during this period

Only takes 1 Degen to win...

assets.name: CheckMates #8
assets.description: CheckMates is an AI-powered chess game. Each NFT represents a fixed game, played by an artificial intelligence system.

asset_contract.name: CheckMates
asset_contract.description:
I developed an AI that simulates a chess game, your unique NFT will make unique moves and eventually get a check mate.

Check mates will display as a forever playing chess game between two AI's. The winning side will be displayed in the traits as will the amount of moves played to win.

Your NFT is unique, because you receive a chessboard  between 10^43 and 10^50 positions, but with the AI playing a regular chess game, it will play until it gets check mate.

assets.name: Circle of Frens #7817
assets.description: This is a generative art project that pays homage to the distinctive styles of a diverse group of artists by using the color gradient from their artworks and combining them through a series of interleaving concentric circles. assets.name: Frenly Panda #1914
assets.description: Frenly Pandas is a community driven collection of 10,000 unique and randomly generated NFTs on the Ethereum Blockchain.

asset_contract.name: Frenly Pandas
asset_contract.description:
Welcome to Frenly Pandas! 

A dynamic community of NFT holders who believe in the power of:

 Community
 Abundance 

At Frenly Pandas, we believe in the principles of the gift economy , where value is created through the exchange of gifts, resources, and knowledge. Unlike the gift economy in the "real world," the value created in the NFT space is held in a monetary fashion through the value of the token going up .

By owning a Frenly Panda token, you not only unlock:

 Exclusive perks 
 Benefits 
 Resources 

But you also become a part of a community that operates on the principles of mutual support , abundance , and generosity . When you gift a Frenly Panda token, you give the gift of empowerment , including:

 Tools 
 Resources 
 Education 
 Community support 

Learn more at FrenlyPandas.org

assets.name: Circle of Frens #8480
